reviews.text:
New Decathlon had opened here! Nice spot to spend a weekend with kids and family.
But the mall is quite old and the toilets are dirty, wish the management could improve that.

Smallsr mall that caters more for the locals over here. Has a decent set market with fresh veg, meat and fish.

Good place to use post office and HK hockey club and also a major bus terminus.
A good mall for shopping. Sometimes items are available with good discounts.

Very nice place and convenient place to shop at reasonable price... for ladies who are frequent shopaholic for them there are lots of variety of tops n shoes which is at affordable price and Meyer stationery shop for all types of kids all have some type of toys too
It's good when u haven't been there for ur millionth time
